OL,3,CManchester man given hospital order
OL,4,Cafter murder of Michelle Hopkinson
OL,6,FA man from Droylsden in Greater
OL,7,FManchester has been sentenced to a
OL,8,Fhospital order 'with restrictions',
OL,9,Fafter stabbing a stranger to death.
OL,11,FPaul Hughes bought a pack of kitchen
OL,12,Fknives and waited down a canal path
OL,13,Fbefore he stabbed 51-year-old Michelle
OL,14,FHodgkinson, on 2 June last year.
OL,16,FDespite the best efforts of emergency
OL,17,Fservices and those who tried to give
OL,18,Ffirst aid, Michelle died from her
OL,19,Finjuries.
