OL,6,FHughes was suffering from a
OL,7,Fschizophrenic attack at the time of
OL,8,Fthe incident and still is suffering
OL,9,Ffrom Schizophrenia. He was deemed too
OL,10,Fmentally unwell to stand trial.
OL,12,FThe court heard that despite being
OL,13,Funwell, Hughes planned the attack by
OL,14,Fpurchasing a four-piece kitchen knife
OL,15,Fset from a superstore in Tameside,
OL,16,Fbefore getting the tram back to
OL,17,FDroylsden.
