OL,6,FA short time later at midday on 2
OL,7,FJune, he was seen on CCTV walking
OL,8,Ftowards the towpath near Ashton Canal
OL,9,Fbefore taking out the knives from the
OL,10,Fmulti-pack and throwing away the other
OL,11,Fthree knives and packaging.
OL,13,FHughes appeared to be lying in wait
OL,14,Fand waiting for somebody to walk past
OL,15,Fhim.
