OL,3,CManchester man given hospital order
OL,4,Cafter murder of Michelle Hopkinson
OL,6,FAt the same time as Hughes was
OL,7,Fwaiting, Michelle Hodgkinson walked
OL,8,Fpast while on her way to meet her
OL,9,Fmother. He followed her and attacked
OL,10,Fher from behind, stabbing her multiple
OL,11,Ftimes.
OL,13,FThe attack was captured after drivers
OL,14,Fcame forward with dashcam footage of
OL,15,Fthe incident, along with statements
OL,16,Ffrom witnesses.
OL,18,FDetectives then pieced together a
OL,19,Fstrong case to take to court, and
OL,20,FHughes was arrested on 3 June 2023 on
OL,21,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
