OL,4,Cafter murder of Michelle Hopkinson
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Danny Lee of
OL,7,FGMP's Major Incident Team, said:
OL,8,F"Michelle's death has left a void in
OL,9,Fher family, and nothing will fix the
OL,10,Fpain they are feeling. I hope that
OL,11,Fthey can gain some form of closure and
OL,12,Fjustice from the sentence passed today.
OL,14,F"I'd like to thank the members of the
OL,15,Fpublic who rushed to Michelle's side
OL,16,Fand the first responders, both
OL,17,Fparamedics and response police
OL,18,Fofficers who also attended the scene
OL,19,Fto give CPR in an attempt to give her
OL,20,Fthe best possible chance of life.
