OL,6,F"It is a moment to recognise, however,
OL,7,Fthe devastation knife crime causes in
OL,8,Four communities. Across Greater
OL,9,FManchester, officers and staff are
OL,10,Fworking hard to fight, prevent and
OL,11,Freduce this type of crime.
OL,13,FIn a previous tribute to Michelle, her
OL,14,Ffamily have said: "Everyone who knows
OL,15,FMichelle are still in utter shock at
OL,16,Fthe attack she endured and how
OL,17,Fhorrific her last moments were.
