OL,6,F"Our Shelly B was the most amazing,
OL,7,Floving, selfless and funny daughter,
OL,8,Fmother, mother-in-law, sister, auntie
OL,9,Fand most recently a nanna. It was a
OL,10,Fprivilege to have been known and loved
OL,11,Fby her. She loved helping people in
OL,12,Fher community and was known for
OL,13,Fvolunteering as an appropriate adult,
OL,14,Fher charity work and loved creating
OL,15,Fhampers to make people smile.
OL,17,F"She would be there for anyone and the
OL,18,Fday she was taken from us, she was
OL,19,Fdoing just that - walking to meet her
OL,20,Fmum to take her shopping and to go for
OL,21,Fa coffee.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU
