OL,6,F"Our family and friends are
OL,7,Fheartbroken. In one moment our world
OL,8,Fhas crumbled and will never be the
OL,9,Fsame. We will support each other, and
OL,10,Fwe thank and appreciate the love and
OL,11,Fsupport shown by our family and
OL,12,Ffriends. Please hold your loved ones
OL,13,Fclose, tell them you love them and
OL,14,Fmake memories.
OL,16,F"Words cannot describe how much she
OL,17,Fwill be missed. Our biggest
OL,18,Fcheerleader, our confidant, our rock `
OL,19,Fshe will never be forgotten. We love
OL,20,Fyou to the moon and back!
